xcresample_hw.h File Reference

Detailed Description

This header file contains identifiers and register-level driver functions (or macros) that can be used to access the Xilinx Chroma Resampler core.

 MODIFICATION HISTORY:

 Ver   Who     Date     Changes
 ----- ------- -------- -------------------------------------------------------
 4.0   adk     03/12/14 First release
                        Added the register offsets and bit masks for the
                        registers and added backward compatibility for macros.

This macro reads the given register.

Parameters:

RegOffset is the register offset of the register (defined at top of this file)
Returns:
The 32-bit value of the register
Note:
